The American breakfast buffet was OK, but it was same thing everyday.	The morning breakfast buffet is 'american style' serving dreadful bacon and eggs, but a generous amount of cereal, pastries, bread, cheese and meats.	The breakfast food was plentiful but not appetizing at all...the orange juice was strange!!	We did get a breakfast buffet that was good, with a lot of choice.	The breakfast was very good and offered more than just rolls and coffee.	Breakfast buffet good - cereals, fruit, juices, bread, eggs and meat.